  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (ELV)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of performing quantity take-offs from tender requirement by reviewing drawings and technical specification to accurately quantify Bill-of-Materials (BOM).</li>\n  <li>Responsible in liaising with internal project/technical teams, and external vendors/subcontractors as to ensure alignment for our offered bid solutions with compliance to technical specification and project timelines</li>\n  <li>Responsible in working within or to manage the tender closing date and time-extensions</li>\n  <li>In charge of conducting cost analysis for project and maintenance works for bidding purposes, including value engineering to optimize project designs and construction methods to achieve cost-effectiveness</li>\n  <li>In charge of compiling the cost estimation for ELV, BMS solutions and relevant scope of works for the implementation</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with local regulations, codes of practice, and industry standards</li>\n  <li>Prepare tender submission and contract documents including bill of quantities (BQ), datasheets, technical proposal for ELV systems and/or BMS system.</li>\n  <li>Assist &amp; support the sales team for tender submission</li>\n  <li>Take charge of evaluating and comparing quotations from subcontractors and suppliers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Electrical Engineering/ Building Services/ Quantity Surveying or related field</li>\n  <li>Min 3 years of relevant experience in QS for Electrical &amp; ELV systems</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS software, AutoCAD, and quantity take-off software</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
